title: Star Zeit Express 10\21: Soh Cah Toa, Jim Jordan, Brian Laundrie, Michael Bay, China, Home Alone
itunes:title: Star Zeit Express 10\21: Soh Cah Toa, Jim Jordan, Brian Laundrie, Michael Bay, China, Home Alone
description:
In this edition of Star Zeit Express, Jack and Miles discuss the North HS teacher placed on leave for racial insensitivity, Jim Jordan struggling to answer questions at Jan. 6 committee, Brian Laundrie being remains possibly being found, Michael Bay's new film 'Ambulance', China news, and the new 'Home Alone' lego set.
